      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented for your consideration is a superlative example of automotive excellence. This vehicle remains in showroom condition, exhibiting no discernible wear and maintaining its original factory luster. Every mechanical and aesthetic detail has been preserved to the highest standard, offering a driving experience indistinguishable from new. For the discerning collector or enthusiast who demands nothing less than perfection, this specimen represents the pinnacle of its class.",
